00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:54.420
I'm going to come back to this,

00:07:54.420 --> 00:07:57.320
because I think what this image
does is it captures that as much

00:07:57.320 --> 00:08:00.320
of these images certainly
have a place in reminding us

00:08:00.320 --> 00:08:04.190
that North Korea is a
deeply repressive country.

00:08:04.190 --> 00:08:07.060
These images also come
with a deep paradox.

00:08:07.060 --> 00:08:09.750
If we scratch a little bit
