00:08:09.750 --> 00:08:11.810
that the consequence
of our own fascination,

00:08:11.810 --> 00:08:16.800
this strange combination of horror
and pleasure, is that such ways

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:21.060
of writing and visualizing North
Korea, actually reproduce a version

00:08:21.060 --> 00:08:25.660
