00:11:07.300 --> 00:11:11.230 position:56%
Yet our criticism does not challenge
the fundamental narrative framework,

00:11:11.230 --> 00:11:14.490
or offer alternative
sources of historical agency.

00:11:14.490 --> 00:11:18.940
It's difficult to dislodge fixation
with the Kim family and at the risk

00:11:18.940 --> 00:11:22.300
of overstating things,
perhaps it's time that we admit

00:11:22.300 --> 00:11:24.110
that the greatest testament
to the power

00:11:24.110 --> 00:11:27.480
of the personality cult is
it reaches out from Pomnyum

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:31.340
to influence our very own
histories of North Korea.

00:11:31.340 --> 00:11:32.790
This type of circularity

00:11:32.790 --> 00:11:37.380
and analytical dead-end was
once the case with Mow in China.

00:11:37.380 --> 00:11:39.850
Was certainly the case with
Stalin and the Soviet Union,

00:11:39.850 --> 00:11:41.790
