and societies.

00:11:55.970 --> 00:11:58.260
Yet not so with North
Korean history right.

00:11:58.260 --> 00:12:04.370 position:56%
Kim remains transcendent to a
history that he himself makes rather

00:12:04.370 --> 00:12:06.800
