sectors of the economy.

00:19:18.560 --> 00:19:22.940
And this was key to claiming
and all socialist economies

00:19:22.940 --> 00:19:26.880
that they could be more efficient
than the capitalist counterparts.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:31.430
Yet of course such control
was not so straightforward

00:19:31.430 --> 00:19:34.780 position:56%
and we can see this in the
specialty economic journals that are

00:19:34.780 --> 00:19:36.620
in this library's collection.

00:19:36.620 --> 00:19:41.440
The main one of which is called
