00:19:52.490 --> 00:19:56.980
And I want to just cite one
particular piece published in 1959

00:19:56.980 --> 00:19:59.400
by an economist and Kim
en Jong [assumed spelling]

00:19:59.400 --> 00:20:01.040
who is nobody special right?

00:20:01.040 --> 00:20:05.860
