00:23:21.240 --> 00:23:26.510
So, if from the central
perspective, planner sought to deal

00:23:26.510 --> 00:23:30.370
with depressing labor shortage
by trying to balance right

00:23:30.370 --> 00:23:34.260
from a macro perspective
where labor would flow.

00:23:34.260 --> 00:23:37.110
From that micro perspective,
from those managers

00:23:37.110 --> 00:23:41.760
that have this political pressure
on them to increase production,

00:23:41.760 --> 00:23:44.810
they don't care about
central attempts

00:23:44.810 --> 00:23:48.250
to balance labor force
across the country.

00:23:48.250 --> 00:23:51.550
They care about their immediate
need to increase production.

00:23:51.550 --> 00:23:55.810 position:56%
So, their short-term production
